          "$type": "Models.Memo, Models",
          "Text": "Herd management example\n# Rules for selling breeders\n\n## Activity\nActivities.Manage herd.Manage numbers (Ruminant activity manage)\n\n## Properties\n\n- As per Increase breeder example\n\n## additional components\n- Added a Ruminant Group below the Manage ruminants activity with a RemoveFemaleBreeders style\n- Added filters below the ruminant group\n-- IsBreeder FilterByProperty -> Female.IsBreeder IsTrue\n-- AgeDescending SortByProperty -> Age descending\n-- TakeFive TakeFromFilter -> Individuals, 5, from start\n\n## Initial herd\n- 20 female breeders and 2 male breeders\n\n## Results\n-\n\n",
